dataset.title: Further contribution to the knowledge of Georgian species of the Carabus Linnaeus, 1758 subgenus Neoplectes Reitter, 1885, with description of a new subspecies of C. titarenkoi Zamotajlov & Fominykh, 2014 (Coleoptera: Carabidae: Carabini)

abstract.para: This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Fominykh, Dmitriy D., Zamotajlov, Alexandr S.
